  "html": "<div class=\"emendate\"><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Etymology_2\">Etymology</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=emendate&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" title=\"Edit section: Etymology\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3><p>From <i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/emendatus#Latin\" title=\"emendatus\">&#x113;mend&#x101;tus</a></i> <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">&#x201C;</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\">correct, faultless, perfect</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">&#x201D;</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">)</span>, from <i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/emendo#Latin\" title=\"emendo\">&#x113;mend&#x14D;</a></i> <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">&#x201C;</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\">I free from faults, I correct, I improve, I amend</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">&#x201D;</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">)</span> and <i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/-e#Latin\" title=\"-e\">-&#x113;</a></i> <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">&#x201C;</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\">-ly, -ily</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">&#x201D;</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">)</span>.\n</p><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Adverb\">Adverb</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=emendate&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13\" title=\"Edit section: Adverb\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3><p><strong class=\"Latn headword\" lang=\"la\">&#x113;mend&#x101;t&#x113;</